{"id": "cul1665702995473", "title": "Run the Service as a Web Service", "breadcrumbs": ["Installing Uniface", "Installing and Configuring Uniface on iSeries", "Running Uniface Applications on iSeries", "Deploying Server Pages and Web Services on iSeries", "Run the Service as a Web Service"], "url": "https://docs.rocketsoftware.com/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/cul1665702995473.html", "html": "<html><body><header class=\"zDocsTopicPageHead\"><h1 class=\"css-g931ng\">Run the Service as a Web Service</h1><div class=\"zDocsTopicActions\" role=\"list\"><div class=\"zDocsBundlePagination\" data-testid=\"next-prev-container\" role=\"listitem\"><div class=\"zDocsPrevTopicButton zDocsPrevTopicButton\"><span class=\"\"><a aria-label=\"Previous:   Create and Run a Test Service on iSeries \" class=\"\" data-tooltip-content=\"Previous:   Create and Run a Test Service on iSeries \" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" data-tooltip-open=\"false\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/qmw1665702995400.html\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-prev\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-prev\"></use></svg></a></span></div><div class=\"zDocsNextTopicButton zDocsNextTopicButton\"><span class=\"\"><a aria-label=\"Next:   Configuring for Web Deployment on iSeries \" class=\"\" data-tooltip-content=\"Next:   Configuring for Web Deployment on iSeries \" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" data-tooltip-open=\"false\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/qvl1665702996049.html\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></a></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsMyDocsMenu\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-label=\"Add to My Topics\" class=\"d-none d-lg-flex\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" data-tooltip-content=\"Add to My Topics\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" id=\"addToMyDocsDropdownTrigger\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-bookmark-add\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-bookmark-add\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none d-flex\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-bookmark-add\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-bookmark-add\"></use></svg>Add to My Topics</span><div aria-labelledby=\"pdfDropdown\" class=\"dropdown-menu dropdown-menu-right\"><a class=\"zDocsAddTopicButton zDocsMyDocsMenuItem dropdown-item\" href=\"/de-DE/auth/login?redirect=/bundle/uniface_104/page/cul1665702995473.html?finish_action=mydocs_topic_and_sub\">Add selected topic and subtopics</a><a class=\"zDocsAddTopicButton zDocsMyDocsMenuItem dropdown-item\" href=\"/de-DE/auth/login?redirect=/bundle/uniface_104/page/cul1665702995473.html?finish_action=mydocs_topic_and_sub_head\">Add Topic &amp; Subtopics with topic head</a><a class=\"zDocsAddTopicButton zDocsMyDocsMenuItem dropdown-item\" href=\"/de-DE/auth/login?redirect=/bundle/uniface_104/page/cul1665702995473.html?finish_action=mydocs_pub\">Add entire publication</a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsWatchButton\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-label=\"Watch\" class=\"d-lg-flex d-none zDocsSubscribeButton\" data-tooltip-content=\"Watch\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-eye\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-eye\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none d-flex zDocsSubscribeButton\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-eye zDocsSubscribeButton\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-eye\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsSubscribeButton\">Watch</span></span></div><div class=\"zDocsExportPdfMenu zDocsExportMenu\" data-testid=\"export-pdf-menu\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-label=\"Download PDF\" class=\"d-none d-lg-flex\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" data-tooltip-content=\"Download PDF\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-pdf\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-pdf\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none d-flex\" data-return-focus=\"#zDocsTopicActionsMobile\" data-target=\"#ZdExportPDFModal\" data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-pdf\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-pdf\"></use></svg>Download PDF</span><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu\"><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportTopicButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"singlePdf\" role=\"button\">Save selected topic</a><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportSubtopicsButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"pdfWithChildren\" role=\"button\">Save selected topic and subtopics</a><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportBundleButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"wholeBundlePdf\" role=\"button\">Save entire publication</a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicShare zDocsShareButton\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-label=\"Share\" class=\"d-none d-lg-flex zDocsShareDialogButton\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" data-tooltip-content=\"Share\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-share\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-share\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none zDocsShareDialogButton\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-share\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-share\"></use></svg>Share</span><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu\"><a class=\"dropdown-item zDocsShareButton zDocsShareEmail\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\"><span>Email Link</span></a><a class=\"dropdown-item zDocsShareButton zDocsShareLink\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\"><span>Copy Link</span></a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsFeedback zDocsFeedback zDocsTopicFeedback\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-label=\"Feedback\" class=\"zDocsFeedbackButton d-none d-lg-flex\" data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_2526624\" data-toggle=\"modal\" data-tooltip-content=\"Feedback\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none d-flex zDocsFeedbackButton\" data-backdrop=\"static\" data-return-focus=\"#zDocsTopicActionsMobile\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_2526624\" data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Sept 18, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104cul1665702995473.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/cul1665702995473.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/cul1665702995473.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"cul1665702995473\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      Run the Service as a Web Service\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body taskbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">After you have confirmed that the test service <span class=\"ph filepath\">websrv.svc</span> runs correctly, you can deploy it as a web service. To do so, you need to generate a WSDL file that describes the interface to web service clients that wish to invoke the service, and then configure the WRD to use this file.\n </p>\n<section><ol class=\"ol steps\"><li class=\"li step stepexpand\" id=\"cul1665702995473__li_d29270e1_d29271e1_d29272e1\">\n<span class=\"ph cmd\" id=\"cul1665702995473__p_d66671e1_d66672e1_d66673e1\">Create the <span class=\"ph filepath\">.wsdl</span> by running <code class=\"ph codeph\">ide.exe</code> on Windows with the following command line:\n <code class=\"ph codeph\">ide.exe /sto /mwr=ws WEBSRV</code>\n</span>\n<div class=\"itemgroup info\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"cul1665702995473__p_d66674e1_d66675e1_d66676e1\">This creates a file named\n                     <span class=\"ph filepath\">websrv.wsdl</span> in the current directory.</p>\n</div>\n</li><li class=\"li step stepexpand\" id=\"cul1665702995473__li_d29273e1_d29274e1_d29275e1\">\n<span class=\"ph cmd\" id=\"cul1665702995473__p_d66677e1_d66678e1_d66679e1\">Configure the WRD to use this file.\n You must move the file to the <span class=\"ph filepath\">WEB-INF/wsdl</span>IFS directory and (re)build and (re)deploy the <span class=\"ph filepath\">wrd.war</span>file. For more information, see <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"qnb1665702995328.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/qnb1665702995328.html\" title=\"The IBM Integrated Web application server for i can deploy applications that are in the form of a web archive file, .war file or a web application bundle .wab file. The Uniface Web Request Dispatcher (WRD) servlet is not in this format, so it must be packaged into a .war file.\">Configure the WRD and Create a wrd.war File on iSeries</a>\n</span>\n</li><li class=\"li step stepexpand\" id=\"cul1665702995473__li_d29276e1_d29277e1_d29278e1\">\n<span class=\"ph cmd\" id=\"cul1665702995473__p_d66680e1_d66681e1_d66682e1\">Check that the Uniface Soap Request Dispatcher (SRD, included in the WRD jar file) can access it by starting a web browser and entering:\n <code class=\"ph codeph\">http://</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">iSeriesNetworkName</var>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">:10000/uniface/services/websrv.wsdl</code>\n</span>\n<div class=\"itemgroup info\">\n<div class=\"note note note_note\" id=\"cul1665702995473__note_w1826ab1b5b1b5b3b1_w1827ab1b5b1b5b3_w1828ab1b5b1b5_w1829ab1b5b1_w1830ab1b5_w1831ab1\"><span class=\"note__title\">Note:</span> We assume that your port number is 10000 and your context root is\n                     <span class=\"ph filepath\">/uniface</span>.</div>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"cul1665702995473__p_d66683e1_d66684e1_d66685e1\">You should see the contents of the\n                     <span class=\"ph filepath\">wsdl</span> file in your browser. This proves that the SRD is\n                  able to access the file. If you get an error message, the SRD is not able to\n                  access it, so check that the <span class=\"ph filepath\">wsdl</span> file is in the correct\n                  place, and that it is included in the <span class=\"ph filepath\">wrd.war</span> file.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"cul1665702995473__p_d66686e1_d66687e1_d66688e1\">At this point, the service is a web service and can be invoked by web services clients.</p>\n</div>\n</li><li class=\"li step stepexpand\" id=\"cul1665702995473__li_d29279e1_d29280e1_d29281e1\">\n<span class=\"ph cmd\" id=\"cul1665702995473__p_d66689e1_d66690e1_d66691e1\">If you want to test it with Uniface Web services\n               call-out on Windows, you can import the Web service <code class=\"ph codeph\">wsdl</code> by running\n                  <code class=\"ph codeph\">ide.exe</code>: This command reads the <span class=\"ph filepath\">wsdl</span>\n               provided by the SRD on your iSeries and creates a SOAP signature called\n               WEBSRVSERVICE.</span>\n<div class=\"itemgroup info\">\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">ide.exe /sti /mwr=ws http://iSeriesNetworkName:10000/uniface/services/websrv.wsdl</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</div>\n</li><li class=\"li step stepexpand\" id=\"cul1665702995473__li_d29282e1_d29283e1_d29284e1\">\n<span class=\"ph cmd\">Use the same form component to test it. Alter the ProcScript in the command button’s detail trigger:\n </span>\n<div class=\"itemgroup info\">\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">trigger detail \n activate \"WEBSRVSERVICE\".callin(TF1, TF2)\n D1=$status\nend; detail</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</div>\n</li><li class=\"li step stepexpand\" id=\"cul1665702995473__li_d29285e1_d29286e1_d29287e1\">\n<span class=\"ph cmd\">In the [DRIVER_SETTINGS] section of the IDE assignment file <span class=\"ph filepath\">ide.asn</span>, add <code class=\"ph codeph\">SOP = U2.0</code>\n</span>\n</li><li class=\"li step stepexpand\" id=\"cul1665702995473__li_d29288e1_d29289e1_d29290e1\">\n<span class=\"ph cmd\" id=\"cul1665702995473__p_d66692e1_d66693e1_d66694e1\">Start the IDE again, and recompile and test your\n               form in the same way as before.</span>\n<div class=\"itemgroup info\">\n<p class=\"p\"> This time, when you click the button, IDE acts as a web services client and the\n                  following occurs:</p>\n<ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"cul1665702995473__li_d29291e1_d29292e1_d29293e1\">It retrieves the <span class=\"ph filepath\">wsdl</span>\n                     for WEBSRV from the SRD </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"cul1665702995473__li_d29294e1_d29295e1_d29296e1\">Uses it to construct a SOAP message </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"cul1665702995473__li_d29297e1_d29298e1_d29299e1\">Sends it to the iSeries HTTP server </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"cul1665702995473__li_d29300e1_d29301e1_d29302e1\">The IBM i integrated application Server\n                     runs the SRD </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"cul1665702995473__li_d29303e1_d29304e1_d29305e1\">The SRD forwards the request to the UROUTER </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"cul1665702995473__li_d29306e1_d29307e1_d29308e1\">The UROUTER starts a USERVER process </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"cul1665702995473__li_d29309e1_d29310e1_d29311e1\">The USERVER instance carries out the\n                     process </li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n</li></ol></section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2526624\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2526624\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Run the Service as a Web Service Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Sept 18, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Run the Service as a Web Service After you have confirmed that the test service websrv.svc runs correctly, you can deploy it as a web service. To do so, you need to generate a WSDL file that describes the interface to web service clients that wish to invoke the service, and then configure the WRD to use this file. Create the .wsdl by running ide.exe on Windows with the following command line: ide.exe /sto /mwr=ws WEBSRV This creates a file named websrv.wsdl in the current directory. Configure the WRD to use this file. You must move the file to the WEB-INF/wsdl IFS directory and (re)build and (re)deploy the wrd.war file. For more information, see Configure the WRD and Create a wrd.war File on iSeries Check that the Uniface Soap Request Dispatcher (SRD, included in the WRD jar file) can access it by starting a web browser and entering: http:// iSeriesNetworkName :10000/uniface/services/websrv.wsdl Note: We assume that your port number is 10000 and your context root is /uniface . You should see the contents of the wsdl file in your browser. This proves that the SRD is able to access the file. If you get an error message, the SRD is not able to access it, so check that the wsdl file is in the correct place, and that it is included in the wrd.war file. At this point, the service is a web service and can be invoked by web services clients. If you want to test it with Uniface Web services call-out on Windows, you can import the Web service wsdl by running ide.exe : This command reads the wsdl provided by the SRD on your iSeries and creates a SOAP signature called WEBSRVSERVICE. ide.exe /sti /mwr=ws http://iSeriesNetworkName:10000/uniface/services/websrv.wsdl Copy Use the same form component to test it. Alter the ProcScript in the command button’s detail trigger: trigger detail activate \"WEBSRVSERVICE\".callin(TF1, TF2) D1=$status end; detail Copy In the [DRIVER_SETTINGS] section of the IDE assignment file ide.asn , add SOP = U2.0 Start the IDE again, and recompile and test your form in the same way as before. This time, when you click the button, IDE acts as a web services client and the following occurs: It retrieves the wsdl for WEBSRV from the SRD Uses it to construct a SOAP message Sends it to the iSeries HTTP server The IBM i integrated application Server runs the SRD The SRD forwards the request to the UROUTER The UROUTER starts a USERVER process The USERVER instance carries out the process Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}